      <title>日本邮政与保险公司一起因收益率较低而推迟债券购买</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-21/japan-post-joins-insurers-delaying-bond-buying-on-lower-yields</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本邮政保险公司与其他主要人寿保险公司一样，在收益率上升之前暂缓购买国内主权债券，因为人们一直猜测世界上最后一个低于零的利率政策将在今年晚些时候结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-21/japan-post-joins-insurers-delaying-bond-buying-on-lower-yields</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2024 23:02:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国证券交易委员会收紧高收益债券监管，因违约和丑闻导致投资下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-21/thai-sec-tightens-high-yield-bond-scrutiny-as-investment-drops-after-defaults</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位高级官员表示，在最近发生的几起违约事件和重大会计丑闻震撼了投机性债务市场后，泰国证券交易委员会正在加强对高收益债券的监管，以增强支付保障和投资者信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-21/thai-sec-tightens-high-yield-bond-scrutiny-as-investment-drops-after-defaults</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
