      <title>巴西国家石油公司董事会成员从巴西石油巨头辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-21/petrobras-board-member-resigns-from-brazilian-oil-giant</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据两名知情人士透露，巴西国家石油公司董事会成员埃弗拉因·佩雷拉·达克鲁斯上周辞去了在巴西国有石油公司的职务。由于此举尚未公开宣布，他们要求匿名。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-21/petrobras-board-member-resigns-from-brazilian-oil-giant</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2024 20:46:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>勒梅尔表示法国电价涨幅不会超过10%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-21/france-s-electricity-price-hike-won-t-exceed-10-le-maire-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国财政部长布鲁诺·勒梅尔在接受电视采访时表示，法国将于 2 月 1 日起将家庭住宅用电成本增加不超过 10%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-21/france-s-electricity-price-hike-won-t-exceed-10-le-maire-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2024 20:02:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着降息押注减少，新西兰元走势可能会转向</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-21/tide-may-turn-for-nz-dollar-as-bets-on-interest-rate-cuts-pared</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对于新西兰元来说，最糟糕的时期可能已经过去，因为乳制品价格上涨和新西兰央行推迟降息应该会支撑新西兰元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-21/tide-may-turn-for-nz-dollar-as-bets-on-interest-rate-cuts-pared</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2024 18:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
