      <title>Dish债权人致函公司指控债务互换欺诈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-21/dish-creditors-send-letter-to-company-alleging-debt-swap-fraud</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Dish Network Corp. 的一群债权人致函该公司董事会，声称这家卫星电视提供商的重组计划非法，并威胁称，如果不撤销交易，将采取法律行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-21/dish-creditors-send-letter-to-company-alleging-debt-swap-fraud</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2024 15:57:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
